snippet.title: According to Amber
snippet.description:
I do live shows with interactive audiences from time to time with Reality T.V. & Trash T.V.  news, gossip, commentary, spoilers,  recap, roasts, trivia, & lots more so make sure you join in on the fun on my next live! I mostly cover Life After Lockup, Love After Lockup, Married at First Sight, Marrying Millions, 90 Day Fiance, 1000 Lb. Sisters, & more coming soon!

I do occasional cash giveaways on some lives! 

**Super chats & Super stickers welcome!

Have occasional co hosts & special guests and sometimes you if you want to join the panel!
Be apart of the panel!! Or if you have some hot tea you want me to spill then email me at: amberkeltner@gmail.com
